   - `CommandInfo { name, description }`
   - `JobHandle { job_id, status:'queued'|'running'|'completed'|'failed'|'cancelled', created_at }`
   - `JobResult { job_id, status, result:any, error:string|null, cost:number, duration_seconds:number, completed_at:string|null }`
