   - `PromptInfo { prompt, sync_basename, language?, context?, expected_outputs?:string[], code?, test?, example? }`
   - `CommandRequest { command, args?:Record<string, any>, options?:Record<string, any> }`
   - `RunResult { success, message, exit_code, stdout?:string|null, stderr?:string|null, error_details?:string|null }`
   - `CancelResult { cancelled, message }`
   - `CommandStatus { running, command:string|null }`
   - `SpawnTerminalResponse { success, message, command, platform, job_id? }`
   - `SpawnedJobStatus { job_id, command, status:'running'|'completed'|'failed'|'unknown', started_at, completed_at?, exit_code? }`

