   - `CodeRange { startLine, endLine, text }`
   - `DiffSection { id, promptRange, codeRanges:CodeRange[], status:'matched'|'partial'|'missing'|'extra', matchConfidence, semanticLabel, notes }`
   - `LineMapping { promptLine, codeLines:number[], matchType:'exact'|'semantic'|'partial'|'none' }`
   - `HiddenKnowledge { type:'magic_value'|'algorithm_choice'|'edge_case'|'error_handling'|'api_contract'|'optimization'|'business_logic'|'assumption', location:{startLine:number;endLine:number}, description, regenerationImpact:'would_differ'|'would_fail'|'might_work', suggestedPromptAddition }`
   - `DiffStats { totalRequirements, matchedRequirements, missingRequirements, totalCodeFeatures, documentedFeatures, undocumentedFeatures, promptToCodeCoverage, codeToPromptCoverage, hiddenKnowledgeCount, criticalGaps }`
   - `DiffAnalysisResult { overallScore, canRegenerate, regenerationRisk:'low'|'medium'|'high'|'critical', promptToCodeScore, codeToPromptScore, summary, sections:DiffSection[], codeSections:DiffSection[], hiddenKnowledge:HiddenKnowledge[], lineMappings:LineMapping[], stats:DiffStats, missing:string[], extra:string[], suggestions:string[] }`
   - `DiffAnalysisRequest { prompt_content, code_content, strength?, mode?:'quick'|'detailed', include_tests?, prompt_path?, code_path? }`
