   - `ArchitectureSyncResult { success, updated_count, skipped_count, results:ArchitectureSyncModuleResult[], validation:ArchitectureValidationResult, errors:string[] }`
   - `GenerateTagsResult { success, tags:string|null, has_existing_tags, architecture_entry:Record<string, any>|null, error:string|null }`
